name: XCTAttachment.ImageQuality
desc: Compression quality options for image-based attachments.

items.name: case original
items.desc: Original image quality, represented as a lossless PNG image.

items.name: case medium
items.desc: Medium image quality, represented as a high quality lossy JPEG image.

items.name: case low
items.desc: Low image quality, represented as a highly compressed lossy JPEG image.
